[13/07/2018 06:12:55] <font color="#0000ff">mi cuerpo.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:12:58] <font color="#0000ff">Llevo tu vaso</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:01] <font color="#0000ff">de agua al puerto,</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:10] <font color="#0000ff">camino y me siguen los ríos.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:14] <font color="#0000ff">Tip-toe, tip-toe.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:14] <font color="#0000ff">Oh-oh-oh.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:17] <font color="#0000ff">Tip-toe, tip-toe.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:24] <font color="#0000ff">Tip-toe, tip-toe.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:24] <font color="#0000ff">Oh-oh-oh.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:31] <font color="#0000ff">Llevo la mano cosida</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:31] <font color="#0000ff">para no herirte,</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:39] <font color="#0000ff">la mano cosida a la boca.</font>
[13/07/2018 06:13:43] <font color="#0000ff">Ando buscando tu casa</font>
