[13/07/2018 06:58:43] <font color="#00ff00">Sin embargo,</font>
[13/07/2018 06:58:43] <font color="#00ff00">la belleza de Samarcanda</font>
[13/07/2018 06:58:46] <font color="#00ff00">no ha durado</font>
