[13/07/2018 07:10:49] <font color="#ffffff">Osh, Osh.</font>
[13/07/2018 07:10:51] <font color="#00ff00">Osh.</font>
[13/07/2018 07:10:54] <font color="#00ff00">Osh, "benzin", Osh, "benzin".</font>
[13/07/2018 07:10:55] <font color="#ffffff">"Da, da".</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:00] <font color="#0000ff">(Truenos)</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:03] <font color="#00ff00">Creo que vamos a contemplar</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:03] <font color="#00ff00">el milagro de repostar</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:06] <font color="#00ff00">en una gasolinera uzbeka.</font>
