[13/07/2018 07:11:18] <font color="#00ff00">en una gasolinera uzbeka</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:22] <font color="#00ff00">va a ser algo extraordinario,</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:22] <font color="#00ff00">un auténtico documento.</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:25] <font color="#00ff00">¡Esto es impresionante!</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:25] <font color="#00ff00">¡Es impresionante!</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:29] <font color="#00ff00">Voy a repostar.</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:32] <font color="#00ff00">Repostar en una gasolinera uzbeka.</font>
[13/07/2018 07:11:32] <font color="#00ff00">Dios mío...</font>
