[13/07/2018 07:14:59] <font color="#00ff00">No, no, no...</font>
[13/07/2018 07:15:01] <font color="#00ff00">"Spasibo", "spasibo"...</font>
[13/07/2018 07:15:01] <font color="#00ff00">No, no.</font>
[13/07/2018 07:15:03] <font color="#00ff00">Uh, uh...</font>
[13/07/2018 07:15:07] <font color="#00ff00">Ya lo sé,</font>
[13/07/2018 07:15:07] <font color="#00ff00">pero es que la leche esa...</font>
